songs.title: See U Soon (Outro)
songs.lyrics:
I hope you're fine, I do not know how I'm doing
You know that I love you, you know that I protect you

My heart is easy to break, only you know how to take care of it
I would like to remind you every day that I love you, but I can not do it

My lips are loose, my spirits are only for you, My eyes cry for you
Is there any way to make the beautiful family we want? Yes, there is
All my strengths are to be by your side, to be happy, to be well

Everything I write to you, everything I do for you, do you appreciate it?
I'm not saying do not do it, I'm just asking

I hope you're fine, I do not know how I'm doing
You know that I love you, you know that I protect you

My heart is easy to break, only you know how to take care of it
I would like to remind you every day that I love you, but I can not do it

My lips are loose, my spirits are only for you, My eyes cry for you
Is there any way to make the beautiful family we want? Yes, there is
All my strengths are to be by your side, to be happy, to be well

Everything I write to you, everything I do for you, do you appreciate it?
I'm not saying do not do it, I'm just asking

Let's run alone, run together, I love you, I appreciate you, I respect you, I take care of you, I miss you, I give you my happiness

Bye take care
